<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes, maximum-scale=2.0">
  <title>Лунный свет | Ты не одна</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: #0a1a1f;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .forest-container {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 720px;
      background: #0b1c24;
      border-radius: 3rem 3rem 2.5rem 2.5rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), 0 0 0 2px rgba(90, 180, 200, 0.25);
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 20%, #1a3a44 5%, #0b1c24 70%);
    }

    .sky-forest {
      position: relative;
      flex: 1;
      width: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0b2833 0%, #0f2a2f 40%, #142f2b 100%);
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .moon {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 28%;
      aspect-ratio: 1/1;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #fffde7, #f7e9c3 30%, #e6d7a3 80%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 0 70px rgba(255, 250, 210, 0.9), 0 0 140px rgba(240, 220, 140, 0.7), 0 0 200px rgba(200, 200, 120, 0.5);
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .moon::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 25%;
      left: 25%;
      width: 20%;
      height: 20%;
      background: rgba(180, 160, 110, 0.4);
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 35px 15px 0 -2px rgba(160, 140, 90, 0.5), 10px 45px 0 1px rgba(150, 130, 80, 0.5), -10px 30px 0 -3px rgba(170, 150, 90, 0.5);
    }

    .trees {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 65%;
      z-index: 3;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .tree-silhouette {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      background: #0a181c;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    .tree1 {
      left: 5%;
      width: 14%;
      height: 60%;
      background: #081a1b;
      border-radius: 40% 60% 0 0;
      box-shadow: 5px -10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    }
    .tree2 {
      left: 22%;
      width: 12%;
      height: 70%;
      background: #0c1e1f;
      border-radius: 30% 70% 0 0;
    }
    .tree3 {
      left: 38%;
      width: 16%;
      height: 75%;
      background: #091817;
      border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0;
      box-shadow: -8px -5px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }
    .tree4 {
      left: 58%;
      width: 14%;
      height: 65%;
      background: #0a1c1d;
      border-radius: 35% 65% 0 0;
    }
    .tree5 {
      left: 75%;
      width: 13%;
      height: 68%;
      background: #081716;
      border-radius: 40% 60% 0 0;
    }
    .tree6 {
      left: 88%;
      width: 12%;
      height: 55%;
      background: #0b1f1e;
      border-radius: 30% 70% 0 0;
    }

    .branch {
      position: absolute;
      background: #0a181c;
      height: 8%;
      width: 25%;
      border-radius: 0 60% 20% 0;
    }

    .fog {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 30%;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(180, 210, 210, 0.15), transparent);
      z-index: 4;
    }

    .content-panel {
      position: relative;
      background: rgba(8, 25, 30, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-top: 2px solid rgba(70, 160, 160, 0.5);
      padding: 1.6rem 1.2rem 1.2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      z-index: 10;
      box-shadow: 0 -10px 30px rgba(0, 20, 20, 0.7);
    }

    .message {
      color: #d4f0f0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-align: center;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 6px #0a2020;
      background: rgba(15, 45, 45, 0.5);
      padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 0.2rem 0 0.4rem;
    }

    .night-btn {
      background: rgba(20, 70, 75, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border: 1.5px solid #3a9090;
      color: #c5f0f0;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 3rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e4f55, #0c353a);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 12px rgba(0, 20, 20, 0.6), 0 0 8px rgba(50, 150, 150, 0.5);
      text-shadow: 0 1px 4px #032020;
    }

    .night-btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #256a70, #134b4f);
      border-color: #6ad4d4;
      color: #e8ffff;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0, 30, 30, 0.9), 0 0 16px #4db8b8;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .night-btn:active {
      transform: translateY(1px);
      box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    .animation-stage {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 120px;
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      overflow: visible;
    }

    canvas {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: transparent;
    }

    .caption {
      color: #aacfcf;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      margin-top: 0.1rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    @media (max-width: 450px) {
      .night-btn {
        padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="forest-container">
    <div class="sky-forest">
      <div class="moon"></div>
      <div class="trees">
        <div class="tree-silhouette tree1"></div>
        <div class="tree-silhouette tree2"></div>
        <div class="tree-silhouette tree3"></div>
        <div class="tree-silhouette tree4"></div>
        <div class="tree-silhouette tree5"></div>
        <div class="tree-silhouette tree6"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="fog"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-panel">
      <div class="message" id="statusMessage">
        Ты в моём сердце, даже за тысячи километров 🌙
      </div>
      <div class="buttons">
        <button class="night-btn" id="hugBtn">🤍 Обнять</button>
        <button class="night-btn" id="replayBtn">🔄 Ещё раз</button>
      </div>
      <div class="animation-stage">
        <canvas id="storyCanvas" width="300" height="120"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="caption">палочки, но тепло</div>
    </div>
  </div>
